- **CLI Commands**:
  - `prisma generate`: Generates Prisma Client based on your schema.
  - `prisma migrate dev --name init`: Creates a new migration and applies it to the database.

- **Latest Versions**:
  - Prisma: [Check latest version on npm](https://www.npmjs.com/package/prisma)
  - Prisma Client JS: [Check latest version on npm](https://www.npmjs.com/package/@prisma/client)

- **Key Config Options**:
  - `batchSize`: Controls the number of records processed in a batch.
    ```json
    {
      "generator": {
        "provider": "prisma-client-js",
        "output": "./node_modules/@prisma/client"
      },
      "datasource": {
        "default": {
          "provider": "postgresql",
          "url": "env(DATABASE_URL)",
          "connectionLimit": 10
        }
      }
    }
    ```
  - `connectionLimit`: Limits the number of concurrent connections to the database.
  - `queryLogging`: Enables or disables query logging for debugging.
